author: Jose Martinez
title: Michael Page (Bellator MMA Fighter) Taunts Opponent With "What Are Those?" Gesture
text:
At Bellator 144 on Friday, Michael Page made quick work of his opponent, Charlie Ontiveros . Prior to the end of the first round, the referee called the fight following a series of devastating elbows which broke Ontiveros' jaw.
But, before Page went to celebrate the victory, which improves his record to 9-0, with his team, Venom went down on one knee, motioned towards Ontiveros' painted toenails and asked, "WHAT ARE THOSE?!?"
If there was any doubt in your mind that Page wasn't doing the "What are those?" gesture, he cleared it up in a video after the fight.
